==Cyrillic alphabet==

===Letter===
'''Ю''', '''ю''' (''italics: Ю, ю'')

# The thirty-second letter of the Russian [[Cyrillic]] alphabet. Its name is '''ю''' (jū) and it is pronounced like the English word '''you'''. It is preceded by [[э|Э]] and followed by [[я|Я]].

